CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 22, 1957, pg. 5 reads: "Honor Worthy Grand Matron - Members of the Order of Eastern Star honored its Worthy Grand Matron, Mrs. Esther Greene with a testimonial banquet at Central Baptist Church, June 17. Left to right: Mrs. Ellen Poole, Johnstown; Herbert Townes, State Grand Master; Mrs. Esther Greene, Worthy Grand Matron of Omega Grand Chapter; Mrs. Rebecca Webb, New York City, and Mrs. Mary Smith, Associate Grand Worthy Matron. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Order of Eastern Star members, from left: Ellen Poole, Herbert Townes, Esther Greene, guest of honor; Rebecca Webb, and Mary Smith, gathered behind banquet table in Central Baptist Church
